{"tid":741480,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林昕雨食兩家茶禮知衰：聽日向何紫綸道歉","createTime":"2018-07-13T16:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T17:05:07.000Z","uid":165824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"746cef2210fde5d0f97580c6f433a47074ae850f","tid":741480,"uid":165824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T16:50:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180713/bkn-20180713211857278-0713_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180713%2Fbkn-20180713211857278-0713_00862_001.html&d=aWLXTKQj1tRetMXIM7PMN9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=04963846\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180713/bkn-20180713211857278-0713_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/004804_da305c55cc48f910a7ba2534be70b87d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F004804_da305c55cc48f910a7ba2534be70b87d.png&h=f14ce4f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/004806_1c3dda77056ed3bbd8d7b80a2549a258.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F004806_1c3dda77056ed3bbd8d7b80a2549a258.png&h=1faf7686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃夏蕙契女林昕雨（Eva）由於「食兩家茶禮」，到《香港小姐》面試又參與《亞洲太平洋國際小姐》選美，最終被《亞洲太平洋國際小姐》發聲明炮轟，而擔任該選美活動的佳麗導師及形象指導何紫綸更明言絕不姑息。 <br />\n<br />\n自事件曝光後林昕雨立即認錯，她透露由於知道何紫綸（Ann）現在怒氣難消，不想火上加油，但她說：「件事真係自己唔啱，Ann教咗我好多嘢，我係銘記於心，好想親口同佢道歉，之前諗住等佢下咗火先搵佢，但係思前想後，要表達誠意，決定聽日登門道歉，負荊請罪，希望佢原諒我，大人不記小人過。」"},{"pid":"981f7a9f0759f18af834a5d6024f01e74b4e2934","tid":741480,"uid":188882,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T16:52:49.000Z","msg":"兩邊都選唔中架la 有乜所謂"},{"pid":"aa78f3eadbd13116937c359106f64f10f084c10e","tid":741480,"uid":165824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"981f7a9f0759f18af834a5d6024f01e74b4e2934","tid":741480,"uid":188882,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T16:52:49.000Z","msg":"兩邊都選唔中架la 有乜所謂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T17:05:07.000Z","msg":"雖然係咁但人哋都告佢"}]}